Kiddwaya has advised Ozo on how to win Nengi’s heart again. Ozo has been trying all he can to make Nengi be his girlfriend to no avail. Kiddwaya, during a chat with Ozo, said he needs to do things to make her jealous. The billionaire son had earlier advised Ozo to work hard and make money if he wants to be with Nengi. He argued Nengi is the type of girl that guys would buy expensive things for. “I think you need to switch up a little bit. Do some things she’s not expecting. Girls need to like you more than you like them,” Kidd told Ozo. Nengi has often stated she can’t be with Ozo due to his calm nature. She said she cannot date a  proper man like Ozo, stating she’s also in a relationship outside the House. 